<h1>@Vte{{}}@HI{{oku}}</h1>

<h2> Formation </h2>

<strong>@Vte{{}}@HI{{oku}}</strong>

<h2> Definition </h2>

<strong>@Vte{{}}@HI{{oku}}</strong> is used to describe the completion of a necessary action by
a given time, the completion of a necessary action in preparation for the next step or keeping
the resultant state as it is.
<p></p>

